headline.print_headline: How the Dow Jones Industrial Average Did Friday
headline.main: How the Dow Jones Industrial Average Did Friday

lead_paragraph: The stock market logged its first weekly loss since early August on Friday after a report showed that retail sales in August rose more than economists had forecast. That reinforced expectations that the Federal Reserve could start hiking interest rates sooner than expected.
